		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Bazinga!<br /><br />It worked!<br /><br />This is what I did.<br /><br />After the the loop that does the PPU writes for the playfield background, I added this:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp;;;turn off scrolling<br />&nbsp; LDA #$00<br />&nbsp; STA $2005<br />&nbsp; STA $2005</div><br /><br />I know that one write to $2005 turns off Vertical Scrolling. Is the second write turning off Horizontal scrolling as well?

		

